# Routing & controllers

- Routes only map URL → middlewares → handler; no heavy logic.
- Controllers read `params/query/body`, call service, return JSON.
- Always `return res.status(...).json(...)` in each branch.
- Don’t mix `res.json(...)` and `next()` in the same success path.
- Never `throw` strings; throw `Error` (or your project error classes).
